{"tid":1237613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好當義士係condom","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:05:30.000Z","uid":106870,"like":209,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"61b57a19724cf190dc982fd6e11691278dd0ae1a","tid":1237613,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記政府喺6.9百萬人遊行之後完全冇讓過步，佢哋之所以去到今日進退失據既地步完全係因為6.12義士流既血。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，當人衝既人都有被捕既心理準備。非法集結？預咗，但一定唔係暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n衝既大學生，甚至中學生都唔撚係鬼，全部都係香港人中最熱愛呢片土地既人。求下大家唔好放棄抗爭，唔好放棄呢班年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.12冇人暴動</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回逃犯條例</span></span>"},{"pid":"446a6e95665402cb98d742d0750b09db5f1cd5fc","tid":1237613,"uid":120729,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:09:24.000Z","msg":"冇人係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74b56b5b1a357aad36655b511e1ab53f5d81643","tid":1237613,"uid":54181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e65fc1a7e1ebdc249063b6a6ca231ac788f39e86","tid":1237613,"uid":28741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"黑警才是暴徒<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"f4b4047b4bc788b50f3911f270cd0660dec358d5","tid":1237613,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddc4f4f94e82824e305b025b66996aaaf76742a6","tid":1237613,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18f21448f54c99b30d5730b2ba4c367ffddf805d","tid":1237613,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0f91c1b9bfa2572c6bfa31ddb692c262a98ef37","tid":1237613,"uid":36470,"like":0,"disl